social_posts.post_text: Happy #WinterHouse day! ❄️ Chatted with @lindshubbs about her unexpectedly dramatic visit to Vermont — what she really thinks about Austen’s story of Kyle and Amanda’s wedding night and where things stand for them now + the confusion over her relationship timeline with Carl, why she “cried every day for three weeks” after filming and her reaction to Jess slamming her looks is all unpacked at the link in bio 🔗 We also talk wedding plans, if certain co-stars will make the guest list after all that #WWHL and #SummerHouse drama, and @lukegulbranson *sort of* makes a surprise appearance 📞

Pour yourself a cockie, because #RHOM is back 🦩 Dropping a chat a day leading up to Thursday’s season 5 premiere, kicking things off with @marysolpatton, who teases a major OG breakup by season’s end 👀 we unpack that + why she now trusts someone LESS than Nicole, the Lisa divorce drama (Lea Black cameo included) and a little bit of #RHUGT 🔗 Linked in story/bio!

It’s OG vs. newbies in a whole new way on season 5 of #RHOM 🦩 at least, according to @alexiae_says — we dive into the drama to come, from unexpected feuds, friendship breakups, Lisa’s divorce/Lea Black’s cameo (Alexia has a lot of *thoughts* on that one) + married life, an update on the boys — and if you watch the video, some #RHUGT talk and an answer to those rumors Alexia is selling her Miami pad 🔗 It’s all at the link in story/bio.

One day until #RHOM is back! 🦩@realadrianademoura is spilling on all the "twists and turns" to come in season 5, from OG friction, her relationship with Larsa and Lisa's dramatic divorce -- @leablackmiami cameo included 👀 Why she says the loss of their friendship is her biggest Housewives regret and more is linked 🔗 in my story/bio!

Let’s get it poppin’… or, Pippen? 🦩 @larsapippen isn’t holding back this season on #RHOM — she calls it “Larsa 5.0.” We unpack her new attitude and approach with the ladies, her unexpected feud with Lisa, if she still thinks Julia’s a “weirdo,” the costar she says changed for the worse between seasons and why she’s not labeling her love life right now 🔗 that and more is at the link in story/bio!

“We throw down hard, but bounce back higher.” @heathergay shares where she thinks #RHOSLC goes after San Diego, including how she’s gearing up for the soon-to-tape reunion and the over-under of Jen making an appearance at the all-cast sit-down. Plus, we dive into her #BelowDeckAdventure experience, letting her freak flag fly in Norway and why she wants to see @meredithmarks on a zip-line. Link in story/bio for the full chat!

It’s a very Kathy Christmas 🎄 Got a peek inside the house of Hilton, where Kathy has 35 years worth of holiday collectibles on display — and now, a special bottle of @casadelsoltequila, courtesy of @garcelle! We tour Kathy’s wreath-making station (@badgalriri shoutout, included), discuss her future on #RHOBH 💎 and those headline-making moments at the #PCAs 🔗 More is linked in my story/bio.

Another season of #WinterHouse has come and gone — unpacked the winter that was with @amandabatula and @ciaramiller___, including all the drama with Lindsay and where things stand (or don’t) now. We also get into why there’s no #WinterHouse reunion and so much more at the link in story/bio.

Get ready for a “chaotic, emotionally exhausting doozy” of a #SummerHouse season — at least, that’s how @ciaramiller___ and @amandabatula sum up what’s to come on season 7. What’s *not* coming back to the Hamptons, though, is Austen Kroll — click the link in bio/profile for Ciara’s thoughts about the #SouthernCharm star and more from the season that was on #WinterHouse.
Not the worst year.

I know there’s some *other* Housewives news happening today… but if you need a little counter programming or something to watch while you wait, check out my chat with @kenya — we unpack her time filming #SpecialForces, why she’d rather go through military training again over going on another #RHOA trip ever, which of her fellow peach-holders would epically fail at the challenges and more, including some teases for season 15 👀🍑 She’s also got plans for world domination and a Marvel role in 2023 🔗 Its all linked in story/bio!

@brandiglanville is back on our screens THIS WEEK with #TheTraitors on @peacocktv 📺 *and* she’s headed on another #RHUGT… then, maybe picking up a diamond again??? 💎 She weighs in on @lisarinna’s #RHOBH exit, LVP tweeting about it and all the rumors floating around that they’re both headed back to the 90210. Chat is linked in story/bio 🔗

Cheers to Camille 🥂 Broke down @fraserolender’s decision to fire his troublesome stew and what it means for season 10 of #BelowDeck 🛥️ We get into what he did and didn’t know about Camille’s onboard antics, the Alissa of it all (and if she *really* needed to pull sheets from the guest cabin where Camille was having a meltdown), Captain Sandy vs. Captain Lee and more at the link in story/bio 🔗

I feel like #SouthernHospitality just started, but the finale’s already here 🥲 Chatted with @madison_reese and @glillyvibes to break down the season that was; they share friendship *and* relationship updates and call out the co-stars who surprised them (in a bad way) with their confessionals. Plus, we talk #PumpRules comparisons, their hopes for season 2 🤞🏼… and peanut butter. 🔗 It’s all linked in story/bio.

“I get to do it in a robe on Zoom and make more money.” @teddimellencamp is laughing all the way to the bank thanks to her haters fueling constant conversation about her online, more than 2 years after her #RHOBH exit. We talk taking on the trolls and finding reinvention thanks to @two.ts.inapod — plus, her reality TV future and that speculation/fear a Bravo comeback is coming. 🔗 Link in story/bio for that and more, like the one Housewife Teddi *never* wants as a guest on the pod.

#RHONJ hits “the lowest of low” for @melissagorga this year — we sat down to unpack the season to come, why it’s “the worst it’s ever been” between Melissa, Joe and Teresa and why she doesn’t see reconciliation in their future. Plus, her take on how she got on the show constantly being a topic of discussion, her response to those who say she does nothing but talk about her sister-in-law, some social media activity explanations and more 🔗 Link in story/bio to watch and read + a house tour to come soon 🏡

@teresagiudice is reflecting on her side of the #RHONJ family feud — and she agrees with Melissa on one thing: it’s time to cut the toxicity out of their lives. We dig into what’s to come in season 13, and how binging the past 10 seasons has Teresa seeing her issues with her brother in a whole new light 👀 link in story/bio for our full chat, including what she thinks of the newbies and her reaction to her ex calling her out in the comments section.

#PumpRules is back tomorrow! Sat down with @musickillskate to discuss how she landed on the decision to divorce Tom, how she told him and the aftermath since — including *that* kiss 💋 heard ‘round West Hollywood. I’ve seen the premiere and season 10 feels like a return to form for our SUR-vers 🔗 link in story/bio for the full convo.

#BadMormon is out in the world and #RHOSLC fans will gain a whole lot of insight into @heathergay and how she operates on the show when they read it. We sat down to talk revealing temple secrets, why Outer Darkness is worse than hell and where Housewives goes in a post-Jen Shah world. The book reveals the reality behind the show… some bonds aren’t what they seem. 🔗 Link in story/bio for our full Q&A!

Loverboy no more! @carlradke reveals he’s no longer working for the company (he’s still an investor, though) and it’s a decision/journey we’ll see play out on season 7 of #SummerHouse 🏡 Part 1 of my chat with Carl and @lindshubbs is linked in my story/bio — we talk what’s next and their wedding plans. I’ll share more (including Lindsay discussing the Danielle stuff 👀) on Monday.

It’s #SummerHouse premiere day and @lindshubbs is still trying to unpack what all happened while filming season 7. She admits to being confused by her fallout with Danielle, and will be watching to see when exactly things took a turn for her former BFF. We talk her hopes for their future, why they currently have “no communication” and how she and Carl are feeling about their future on the show. It’s all linked in story/bio + we discuss some unexpected drama between RadHouse and Mya Allen that kicks off in episode 1.

@dolorescatania is “baffled” by her drama with Jennifer Aydin this season on #RHONJ — why it feels one-sided, why she’s not engaging and where things stand now is all unpacked at the link in story/bio 🔗 We also dive into the “sad” Melissa/Teresa split and whether Dolores thinks they can exist on the show together moving forward, Teresa’s reunion with Jacqueline and living in her own love bubble with Paulie 🥰

The doctor is in! @drnicolemartin reflects on her #RHOM journey so far and why she fears history is repeating itself when it comes to the show 🦩 We unpack the “intense” reunion, Andy vs. Larsa, the OG divide and so much more — Nicole gets to hit back at many, many comments made about her on and off the show this season 🔗 Link is in my story/bio!

@kate_chastain is counting down the days (80, if you’re wondering) until she can have a martini 🍸 Caught up with our favorite #BelowDeck alum to talk all things pregnancy, from what/why she is and isn’t sharing on this journey to the type of mom she hopes to be and what @captain_lee_rosbach’s reaction was to her news! Plus, we get into #TheTraitors with a special message from @rachelereillyvillegas ahead of the cast reunion, taping tomorrow 👀 See that above + check out the link in my story/bio for all of Kate’s musings on motherhood.

@imkylecooke shares his side of the Loverboy breakup and reflects on the “awkward” start to season 7 of #SummerHouse 🔗 Full chat linked in story/bio — Kyle reveals the timeline to Carl’s exit from the business and explains where they stand now, sheds some insight on the Lindsay vs. Danielle drama… and defends his mullet.

@danielleolivera shares her side of the story when it comes to falling out with Lindsay Hubbard on season 7 of #SummerHouse — why they landed at a place “beyond repair,” where they stand now and what Danielle hopes for their future is all unpacked at the link in story/bio. Danielle hits back at theories floated by her castmates about the friendship breakup and promises fans will see new sides of her she’s never been able to share before in upcoming episodes.

@lalakent is hitting back at Tom Schwartz and Tom Sandoval’s digs and so much more from this season of #PumpRules — we get into why it’s weird watching back who she was last summer, where she and Randall stand/don’t stand now and what exactly she’s fighting for when it comes to Ocean. Lala also weighs in on the Schwartz/Raquel/Scheana situation 👀 it’s all linked in my story/bio.

A little #PumpRules for your Monday — @scheana gets emotional over her drama with Katie, especially Katie’s “watch your world burn and smile” moment. Why she’s so upset over it and her defense of getting involved in the Schwartz/Raquel saga is all unpacked at the link in story/bio + @kristinakelly shares what it’s been like stepping back into the proverbial SUR alley as someone who’s soon to join the Vander-crew moms club.

Five seasons into her #RHONJ run and @jenniferaydin says she’s done building bridges, because all anyone else does is burn them 🔥 we unpack all the season 13 goings on, from Melissa becoming “collateral damage” in Jennifer’s attempt to expose Margaret, her feud with Dolores, “Tre Soldier” status, to marriage and family — it’s all at the link 🔗 She also reacts to learning a certain Housewife from another city says Jennifer “bugs the s**t out of” her 👀

Get ready for Lisa 2.0! @lisahochstein is ready to find her happy again amid her ongoing divorce, which she admits has “no end in sight.” We talk what’s next and her hopes for how things shake out with Lenny + her new guy, biggest lessons learned from the past year and where she wants the #RHOM group to go after a “really bad” reunion. 🔗 it’s all linked in my bio/story!

@officialxscape is still kickin’ it with #TheQueensofRB — but some of the members could’ve been kickin’ it with @kandi over on #RHOA 🍑 We got into that + so much more, including what it was like joining forces with @officialswv for a one-night-only event… and cameras capturing all the behind-the-scenes drama 🎥 The show premieres Sunday on @bravotv + check out @entertainmenttonight tonight for more from my chat with both iconic groups.

@officialswv is ready for the Bravoholics, because they *are* Bravoholics! #TheQueensofRB premieres tonight — @entertainmenttonight took the ladies of SWV on a little trip down memory lane with a flashback to their first interview in 1993.

Take a break from the Scandoval and check out my chat with @therealmargaretjosephs, breaking down all the drama with her ex-bestie and the “weirdo” meeting she had with Jennifer and Teresa. Margaret establishes a timeline for the whole ordeal, alleging Teresa attempted to get her former friend a spot on #RHONJ after two failed attempts by Marge herself. She hits back at everything Jen’s said about the situation and teases the “big twist” coming by finale. 🔗 It’s all linked in story/bio!
👸🏻 @kristinakelly has always been the voice of reason on #PumpRules

A break from Scandoval and our regularly scheduled Bravo content for a #YouNetflix moment 🚨 SPOILERS AHEAD 🚨 as @pennbadgley reacts to Joe’s season 4 fate and the end that could come in season 5… 🔗 link in bio for more post-finale talk.

@rachelfuda is owning it! The #RHONJ newbie explains her BravoLover1234 account and what she was *really* doing with it. We unpack that and so much from season 13 — from what she made of Jennifer and Teresa’s warning about Margaret, why she doesn’t engage with Jennifer, the wedding drama, Jenn Fessler’s menu ordering rules and more 🔗 it’s all discussed at the link in bio/story!

Filming the show is one thing, watching it back is another 📺 @gabbyprescod shares her reaction to a convo she had no idea went down between Ciara and Mya (about her) on #SummerHouse + we unpack the season so far and what’s still to come, how she’s navigated the cast divides and balanced friendships with both Danielle and Lindsay. That and more (including why Kory is “dangerous and destructive” once he arrives) is at the link in bio/story 🔗

@daniellecabralofficial says Teresa and Jennifer’s warning about Margaret proves itself true, sooner rather than later, on #RHONJ 👀 We discuss that + her feud with Jackie and its origins, navigating the Teresa vs. Melissa of it all (and how she feels about being called a “soldier”), why she doesn’t even buy her own story about her brother drama and more 🔗 It’s all unpacked at the link in story/bio!

I had to fill @therealcandiace in on all things #Scandoval and #PumpRules — and she has some words of encouragement for Ariana. Our full chat about #RHUGT and #RHOP coming tomorrow… but enjoy this for now.

#RHUGT is here! @therealcandiace is spilling all on her time in Thailand and why it “did not end well” for her and fellow #RHOP ‘Wife Gizelle 👀 We get into that + some lingering thoughts on the RHOP reunion and it’s Robyn-filled aftermath, why @leahmob was Candiace’s “MVP” of the trip, what her cryptic pregnancy tweet was *really* about and so much more 🔗 It’s all linked in my story/bio.

Bye, ashy and hello, Thailand! @porsha4real is back in the Bravo-sphere with #RHUGT and all feels right in the world. We discuss replacing Tinsley on the trip, why now was the time to revisit to the world of Housewives and what it would take for a #RHOA return. Plus, how she feels about Candiace questioning her relationship, how marriage has changed things for her and Simon and why Leah was a “disappointment” on the vaca 🔗 it’s all at the link in story/bio… a long with an interview interruption courtesy of some bees in Porsha’s backyard 🐝

@jackiegoldschneider hits back at/explains @dolorescatania’s #RHONJ after-show shade and breaks down all the season 13 drama so far — from facing off with Danielle, to shutting down speculation she was competing for a full-time slot, where the group can go when it’s so divided and why her commentary about not wanting Margaret as an enemy is different from Teresa and Jennifer’s warning that Margaret makes “a better friend than an enemy” is all unpacked at the link in story/bio 🔗

@garcelle has some *thoughts* on her son Oliver’s #PumpRules makeout session and the Scandoval of it all 👀 Plus, her upcoming cameo on the show and if LVP’s agreed to repay the favor with a #RHOBH pop-in 🎥 Cameras were up last night and there’s more from our chat at the link in bio/story, including her reaction to Denise, Camille and Cynthia’s appearances and (potential?) new castmate Annemarie

The showgirl’s headed to Sin City ✨ @theprettymess teases an exciting Las Vegas announcement + shares what filming #RHOBH is like in a post-Rinna world… including facing Dorit’s reaction to her #WWHL prediction at #BravoCon that she and PK would be the next Bravo-lebs to split 👀 That and more is discussed at the link in story/bio!

@kimrichards11 is back in Beverly Hills! She and @kylerichards18 explain how Kim’s #RHOBH return came to be — it’s a day-by-day situation for now — and their hopes for their family after last year’s tough season between Kyle and Kathy. More from our chat is linked in story/bio 🔗

@suttonstracke is celebrating four years of @thesuttonconcept and sharing how she formed a friendship with @cynthiabailey! Plus, she reacts to rumors @jennifertilly will be a “friend of” on #RHOBH and — if you click the link in story/bio — she shares how filming’s going after Rinna’s exit, including who’s stirring the pot.

@meredithmarks brought a little ice to Beverly Hills last night as #RHOBH cameras rolled 🎥 She shared her hopes for #RHOSLC moving forward after season 3 left the cast more divided than ever + if a chair’s been pulled out for Mary Cosby’s purse 👜 More is linked in story/bio.

@meghanking says she’s heard some things about the new season of #RHOC that will leave fans SHOCKED 🍊 We also talk the latest in her life, from leaning into exploring herself and helping other women do the same, to the never-ending saga of her co-parenting relationship 🔗 Link to watch in bio/story.

@lindshubbs says her #SummerHouse castmates should be grateful she’s no longer getting activated rather than coming at her for pulling back on partying. We have a conversation about the conversation happening around her, her relationship and her relationship with drinking + Lindsay shares new insight into her issues with Danielle and why their friendship hasn’t been repaired… yet. 🔗 It’s all at the link in story/bio.

@jennfessler had no idea her mozzarella moment would be meme-worthy! We discuss all the surprises of her Real Housewives experience as #RHONJ season 13 heads into “bloodbath” territory, per Jenn. Why she’s predicting an “explosive” reunion, why Margaret’s “arsenal” is “accidental” and more unpacked at the link 🔗 in story/bio!

ICYMI, @samanthafeher and @korykeefer are a couple! Sam breaks down what it’s been like sitting on this secret, why they had to keep their romance under wraps and what it was like living through his #WinterHouse experience/the Jess situation when they were already an item. It’s all unpacked at the link in bio/story 🔗 along with more from this season of #SummerHouse, including Sam’s reaction to her boxing trainer fling now being linked to Madonna, what was really going through her head when Mya told her she talks too much and what it’s been like navigating the Danielle-Lindsay fallout.

It’s #BelowDeckSailing day! ⛵️ @daisykelliher87 breaks down her love triangle with @king_gk and @parlayrevival_colin and how that changes the dynamics aboard Parsifal III. She reacts to Gary being jealous of her makeout session(s) with Colin and shares where she stands with both men now + explains why this season almost broke her 👀 It’s all at the link in story/bio! @belowdecksailing

@king_gk explains his jealousy of @daisykelliher87 and @parlayrevival_colin’s boat-nance, as @capt_glennshephard reveals whether he’s #TeamGary or #TeamColin 👀 We unpack that and more from season 4 of #BelowDeckSailing at the link in story/bio 🔗

Fantasy. Love. Escape. Bliss. Glamour. Fun. ✨ That’s how @theprettymess describes Erika Jayne — and now she can add Vegas Showgirl to the list 🎰 EJ’s headed to Sin City for her Bet It All on Blonde residency. Tonight on ET — why now was the time to do it, her message to the critics who say she has other things to focus on than performing and what her #RHOBH co-stars make of this major move 💎

@paige_desorbo reacts to criticism over this season of #SummerHouse and fan calls to pivot the show to follow the cast’s lives in NYC. Plus, how she feels about being labeled a “mean girl” and “bedsore girl,” to where she and @caconover stand after their emotional “New York or nowhere” chat, how much we’ll see her pop up on the new season of #SouthernCharm, feeling no FOMO over missing #WinterHouse season 3 and more is unpacked at the link in story/bio 🔗

@kenya previews the mess to come on #RHOA season 15 — she’s labeling one of her co-stars Gru (as in the Despicable Me villain), because she’s apparently got a minion or two working for her… and Kenya’s not mincing words (or really saying any) about her. Plus, the latest in her divorce saga (she shuts down a big rumor), dating, facing off with Shereé’s new guy, @cynthiabailey’s return and why this season feels like a shift away from sisterhood 🔗 It’s all linked in story/bio.

@shereewhitfield hits back at her castmates’ concerns over her new man and more from season 15 of #RHOA 🍑 Why she calls the group’s suspicions of Martell “bulls**t,” why she’s not labeling their romance and how she feels about gossip in general — it’s all unpacked at the link in story/bio, along with Shereé’s take on becoming a “glam-ma.” More from this chat to come tomorrow with @marlohampton

@marlohampton is even more drained after filming season 15 of #RHOA 🍑 Why she’s calling it “epic” and taking credit for “activating” Kandi is all unpacked at the link in story/bio 🔗 We talk her feud with Kenya, her break from the boys and why her life coach hasn’t quite broken Marlo of all her bad habits… at least not yet.

Get ready for #SummerHouseMV! Roped in a little help from @paige_desorbo to welcome @callmecooper_ and @jasmineelliscooper to the #SummerHouse and @bravotv fam 🔗 Check out the link in bio/story for our full chat, including what the Coopers learned about themselves and each other by doing reality TV + Jasmine’s message to the dog lovers of the world (which will make sense once you watch Sunday’s premiere 🐶)

Unhinged. Raw. Delusion. These are just some of the words @myallen and @ciaramiller___ used to describe the #SummerHouse drama and reunion 👀 Their unfiltered feedback on Danielle’s reaction to Carl and Lindsay’s engagement, why some people might be worse off after reunion and where this group goes from here + launching @codependents_, talking topics the show doesn’t cover and why the bed is the best place to be, we get into it all at the link in bio/story 🔗

@lisavanderpump compares the upcoming #PumpRules reunion to running the @vanderpumpdogs center 🐶 We discuss what she made of the day and where things go from here with Sandoval and Raquel, plus more at the link in bio.

@itsjameskennedy says the "No. 1 Guy in the Group" title has him feeling like Tony Stark. We talk his #PumpRules reunion feelings, why he invoked the terms "poo-poo heads" and "worm with a mustache," plus where things can go from here with Sandoval and Raquel. His answer is a surprise. Link in bio for full chat!

People forget, @paulaabdul is a Bravo-lebrity in her own right and I got to sing the praises of #HeyPaula to her at the @vanderpumpdogs gala, where she was searching for Scandoval answers from the #PumpRules crew. Plus, she explains why joining #RHOBH isn’t for her.

🚨 SPOILERS AHEAD 🚨 If you’ve already binged through season 6 of #SellingSunset (the best yet IMO), I unpacked all the Nicole drama with @chrishell.stause — lots of fourth-wall breaking context that fills in those holes, a compliment to Christine ‼️ and if she ever got eyes on those drug test results — and what’s to come in season 7.  Plus, an update on her friendship with Mary after that emotional finale convo. 🔗 It’s all at the link in bio + story!

🚨 SPOILERS AHEAD 🚨 Sat down with @bre_tiesi to unpack her debut season of #SellingSunset — she found watching the episodes proved a little eye-opening, with — she says — one major plot point wholly misrepresented. How she feels about all the focus on her personal life and partner, what she wants to showcase in the future and how she feels about Chelsea after everything that went down is at the link in story/bio + Chelsea’s side coming to your screens Monday.

@trixiemattel endorses RuPaul forgetting #DragRace stars’ and series names at the @vanderpumpdogs gala — she’s become BFFs with @lisavanderpump, bonding over their blissful ignorance of each other’s reality TV worlds. Trixie’s headed back to TV soon with more @queenoftheuniverse + I asked if there’s more @trixiemotel in the works 👀 Link in bio for that + more!

“I think she wants to kill me.” That’s what @chelsealazkani has to say about the status of her relationship with @bre_tiesi after the events of #SellingSunset season 6 — she admits some regret over how she handled things, but also stands by the fact that she doesn’t lie. We also discuss Chrishell vs. Nicole, Christine’s comments about the show/cast since her exit, the fashions and whether Chelsea’s actually British at the link in story/bio 🔗
In honor of Ariana moving out + #PumpRules reunion week, here’s @mrjerryoc’s plea for Sandoval to also get out of the house.

Tonight on ET — we play the Newlywed Game with @teresagiudice and @louiearuelas ahead of their wedding special! Plus, what went down at reunion, what’s next for their #RHONJ and reality TV journey and more 📺 I’ll link full chat in my bio.

It’s @teresagiudice’s wedding day! Well… at least on TV 📺 After tonight’s special episode of #RHONJ comes reunion, and judging by what Teresa and @louiearuelas told me? We’re in for quite the show (or, three, since it’s three parts!) Our full chat about their big day, what goes down at the reunion and if they want a spinoff is in the link in story/bio 🔗

From slinging chicken fingers at @raisingcanes to slaying Sandoval at reunion — today’s a big day for @arianamadix and #PumpRules. What she’s claiming for herself in this moment of opportunity, her future plans for the show, @somethingabouther and more all discussed at the link in bio.

Happy #RHONJ reunion day! @daniellecabralofficial promises chaos and vindication over the next three weeks — she says there’s no winner in the Teresa vs. Melissa feud, believes there’s room for them to coexist on the show moving toward and felt some positivity at the end of the taping. What all is unpacked at reunion, her hopes for the show’s future and some personal life updates all linked in story/bio 🔗

Happy #PumpRules reunion (part 2) day to all who celebrate! In honor of @allylewber joining the crew this week, here’s her reflecting on being the #Scandoval whistleblower 👀 Link in bio to a sneak peek at tonight’s episode.

We’re a day away from #RHOC’s return and the comeback combo of @tamrajudge and @taylorarmstrong — we sat down at @deckonlaguna to unpack what’s to come in season 17. 🍊 Tamra shares the co-star comment that hurt the most surrounding her exit, they agree on the cast member who disappointed them the most and discuss the “reality avoidance” Tamra had to call out 👀 Full convo is linked in my bio/story!

A “very tough” season of #RHOC left @heatherdubrow  feeling like she has PTSD 🤯 We get into why she thinks season 17 “didn’t end well,” where she stands with Tamra (who apparently went “nuclear” on Heather) and why her friendships with Gina and Emily have changed since we last saw them together. Plus, she addresses speculation she’s the reason for the delayed premiere and reveals if selling her Newport Beach mansion means she’s done with the show. 🔗 That and more is linked in story/bio!

Does the #RHOC cast live in fear of @tamrajudge?! @shannonbeador says at least one orange-holder does 👀 We unpack that + how Shannon navigated Tamra’s return, why it was both hard and easy and where they stand now (reunited as the @tresamigasoc with @vickigunvalson!) 🍊 We also talk her next chapter as an empty nester, starting over at 59 and that recent reunion with David 🔗 It’s all linked in bio/story.

“Where is my girl @porsha4real?!” — @drewsidora is here for a #RHOA cast shakeup, ready to reinstate Porsha and @kimzolciak’s peaches for season 16! 🍑 We unpack the mixed fan reaction to season 15, why Drew’s over Marlo and where the cast goes from here, “more divided than ever.” Plus, an emotional chat about what led Drew to file for divorce, how her music is therapy and what she’s claiming for herself in this new chapter. 🔗 It’s all at the link in bio/story.

@larsapippen and @heirmj523 know you have questions about their relationship — it’s one of the reasons why they decided to get into business together and launch their @separation_anxiety_podcast. I sat down with them at home in Miami to unpack the biggest misconceptions about their romance, find out what their families *really* think of it and see where they see this thing going 💍 Link in story/bio to watch + read the full chat. #RHOM
